  • 使用org.springframework.messaging.handler.annotation.support的程序包 
    程序包 说明
    org.springframework.jms.annotation
    Annotations and support classes for declarative JMS listener endpoints.
    org.springframework.jms.config
    Support package for declarative messaging configuration, with Java configuration and XML schema support.
    org.springframework.messaging.handler.annotation.support
    Support classes for working with annotated message-handling methods.
  • org.springframework.jms.annotation使用的org.springframework.messaging.handler.annotation.support中的类 
    类和说明
    MessageHandlerMethodFactory
    A factory for InvocableHandlerMethod that is suitable to process an incoming Message Typically used by listener endpoints that require a flexible method signature.
